channel.title: Dev Team (Not A Joke) Dark Pk
channel.description:
[center][b][size=20pt]Dark Pk[/size][/b][/center]
As every server has it's time and place, mine will to. I am already in posession of a server, forums, and wide, helpful community playing my server. I am the owner/hoster/coder of Dark Pk 24/7, better known as Undark or Totalown. I am looking for an experienced dev team, and I will help in the process. This server will have the following:
[ul][li]Projectiles Fully Functional[/li] [li]Static Icons- Clientside[/li] [li]Finished GS minigame (Half Finished)[/li] [li]Rarely seen in private servers.... QUESTS![/li] [li]Fully working minigames[/li] [li]MySQL (Currently messing with it, hopefully done soon)[/li] [li]Full 484 gameframe- Client (Half Made)[/li] [li]Anti-Lag[/li] [li]Anti-Mass(Already made)[/li] [li]A database on forums, instead of a regular server that we use(If possible)[/li] [li]A self-updating high-scores[/li] [li]A crude version of the Grand Exchange[/li] [li]Fully working minigames[/li] [li]Add new Minigames(Bounty Hunter, Clan wars, etc.)[/li] [li]Fully working Summoning, Hunting, and Construction(Clientside/Serverside)[/li] [li]A 3-4 version of the Barrows/Degrading(Doesn't have to be perfect)[/li] [li]A well formed economy e.g No commands[/li] [li]Tutorial Island (Easy)[/li] [li]Anti-Duplication[/li] [li]Protection against cheat clients[/li] [li]And more...[/li][/ul]
The application code is as follow's:
[code]Age: Name: Msn/Aim: Experience: Any work that you can show: Interests: Time Zone: What languages you know(Programming langs.)[/code]
I am looking for-
---1-2 Server Programmers ---0 Hosters (I'm getting a dedi soon) ---2 Moderator's ---1-2 Administrators ---1-2 Client Programmers ---1 Forums Designer And as many people that want to join my forums (Please don't spam)
[url=http://Www.Darkpk.ipbfree.com]Www.Darkpk.ipbfree.com[/url] or [url=http://Www.Darkpk.co.nr]Www.Darkpk.co.nr[/url]
Server Programmers- Call of Duty
Forums designers- Call of Duty
This server is already prospering, soon it will be a community and home to many.
[b][size=30pt]NO SPAMMING/FLAMING! IT WILL BE REPORTED TO THE STAFF! You are forewarned![/size][/b]
